  preOpLines:
  - speaker: Head Witch
    text: Orren pulled three cooks out before he noticed his own wound.
  - speaker: Orren
    text: I am not leaving my kitchen to the apprentices. Patch me fast.
  surgeryLines:
  - speaker: Head Witch
    text: His bleeding is quicker than Mira's. If your first Fire cast misses, recover
      with Water before trying again.
  - speaker: Head Witch
    text: Close every open wound.
    waitForSpellSelect: 0
    waitForSpellCast: 0
    waitForWoundsCleared: 1
    waitBeforeShowingLine: 1
    transitionToInside: 0
    transitionToPart: 0
